OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FAfter much fanfare and hype, the
OL,7,Fstarter gun for the inaugural Enhanced
OL,8,FGames will finally go off in Las Vegas
OL,9,Fthis weekend for a night organisers
OL,10,Fpromise will go down in history.
OL,12,FDubbed by critics as the "Olympics on
OL,13,Fsteroids", the event permits
OL,14,Fcompetitors to use certain substances
OL,15,Fapproved by the US Food and Drug
OL,16,FAdministration (FDA), including
OL,17,Ftestosterone and growth hormones.
