OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FOrganisers say the Games are designed
OL,7,Fto explore the limits of human
OL,8,Fperformance through science and
OL,9,Fmedicine, but critics argue they
OL,10,Fnormalise drug use in sport and could
OL,11,Fput athletes' health at risk.
OL,13,FAs the competitors get ready to warm
OL,14,Fup, we explore what the Enhanced Games
OL,15,Fare, where they are being held, and
OL,16,Fwhat people can expect.
OL,18,FWhat is the idea behind the Enhanced
OL,19,FGames?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
