OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FFounded in 2023 by Australian
OL,7,Fentrepreneur Aron D'Souza, the Games
OL,8,Faim to challenge conventional sporting
OL,9,Fnorms by "embracing medicine and
OL,10,Fscience to push human potential while
OL,11,Fprioritising safety, transparency, and
OL,12,Finnovation".
OL,14,FThose behind the Games describe it as
OL,15,Fthe "intersection of elite athletics
OL,16,Fand modern medical science".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
