OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FThe 40 competing athletes
OL,7,Fparticipating in the four categories,
OL,8,Fswimming, track, weightlifting and
OL,9,Fstrongman, are allowed to take
OL,10,Fperformance-enhancing drugs, including
OL,11,Fsteroids, testosterone and growth
OL,12,Fhormones, which are typically legal to
OL,13,Fpossess but are banned in competitive
OL,14,Fsport.
OL,16,FAmong the athletes taking part are
OL,17,Fworld champions and record holders
OL,18,Facross multiple disciplines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
