OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FOne of the appeals to athletes is the
OL,7,Fmoney on offer. Unlike traditional
OL,8,Fevents, all athletes are paid, with a
OL,9,F$25 million pot up for grabs,
OL,10,Fincluding a $1million (#739,655) prize
OL,11,Ffor breaking the 50m freestyle world
OL,12,Frecord.
OL,14,FWhere is the event taking place - and
OL,15,Fwhen?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
