OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FThe Games are a one-night-only
OL,7,Fextravaganza in the entertainment
OL,8,Fcapital of Las Vegas in a specially
OL,9,Fbuilt venue in front of 2,500
OL,10,Fspectators, according to the
OL,11,Forganisers.
OL,13,FWhat do experts say are the risks?
OL,15,FCritics argue that the use of
OL,16,Fperformance enhancers crosses an
OL,17,Fethical line, but there are also
OL,18,Fconcerns for the athletes' long-term
OL,19,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
