OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FAccording to USADA, the US Anti-Doping
OL,7,FAgency, performance-enhancing drugs
OL,8,Fcan drastically alter the human body
OL,9,Fand potentially change biological
OL,10,Ffunctions.
OL,12,FDr Catherine Norton, Associate
OL,13,FProfessor Sport & Exercise Nutrition,
OL,14,FUniversity of Limerick, said: "Elite
OL,15,Fsport already places extraordinary
OL,16,Fphysical and psychological demands on
OL,17,Fathletes, and we need to be careful
OL,18,Fnot to further blur the lines between
OL,19,Fhigh performance and high risk."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
