OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FShe says she would be particularly
OL,7,Fconcerned about substances linked with
OL,8,Fcardiovascular, hormonal,
OL,9,Fneurological, and psychological risk.
OL,11,FThose behind the Games said athletes
OL,12,Fare closely monitored.
OL,14,F"Competitors undergo comprehensive
OL,15,Fhealth profiling and ongoing
OL,16,Fmonitoring, and all permitted
OL,17,Fperformance-enhancing substances have
OL,18,Festablished medical uses and robust
OL,19,Fsafety data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
