OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,F"An independent Medical and Scientific
OL,7,FCommission provides guidance and
OL,8,Freinforces a commitment to
OL,9,Ftransparency, athlete safety, and
OL,10,Fadvancing the role of science in
OL,11,Fshaping the future of human
OL,12,Fperformance."
OL,14,FAre there British participants?
OL,16,FReece Prescod won a European silver in
OL,17,F2018 and also competed at the Tokyo
OL,18,FOlympics before retiring in August
OL,19,Flast year, when interest from UK
OL,20,FAthletics and sponsors dried up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
