OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FPrescod told ITV News that, in part,
OL,7,Fhis struggles in retirement led him to
OL,8,Fsign up to the Enhanced Games.
OL,10,FHis decision came under fire from UK
OL,11,FAthletics chief executive Jack
OL,12,FBuckner, who called his participation
OL,13,F"appalling".
OL,15,FIn September 2025, Olympic silver
OL,16,Fswimming medallist Ben Proud was the
OL,17,Ffirst British athlete to announce that
OL,18,Fhe would be participating in the event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
