OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779372669
OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FSwimmer Emily Barclay, who won a gold
OL,7,Fmedal in the 50m freestyle at the 2019
OL,8,FBritish Championships, was named as
OL,9,Fthe latest British athlete to join in
OL,10,FJanuary.
OL,12,FJane Rumble, UK Anti-Doping's chief
OL,13,Fexecutive, said: "It is incredibly
OL,14,Fdisappointing that any British athlete
OL,15,Fwould consider competing in an event
OL,16,Fthat flies in the face of the true
OL,17,Fspirit of sport."
