OL,3,CWhat are the Enhanced Games and why
OL,4,Care they so controversial?
OL,6,FAustralian swimmer and Olympic
OL,7,Fmedallist James Magnussen said in
OL,8,FFebruary 2024 that he intends to come
OL,9,Fout of retirement to compete in the
OL,10,FGames in an attempt to break the 50m
OL,11,Ffreestyle world record.
OL,13,FHow can I watch?
OL,15,FThe one-night spectacle kicks off with
OL,16,Fthe opening events at 6:30 p.m. ET /
OL,17,F11:30 p.m. BST on YouTube.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
